Command Line Tool命令行工具

We've built a CLI (Command Line Interface) which is supported by OSX, Linux and Windows. To create your own resume, install resume-cli from npm:我们构建了一个受 OSX、Linux 和 Windows 支持的 CLI（命令行界面）。要创建您自己的简历，请从 npm 安装 resume-cli：

npm install -g resume-clinpm 安装-g resume-cli

Exporting出口

The command line tool uses an ecosystem of modules that we've open sourced to convert your resume to different formats:命令行工具使用我们开源的模块生态系统将您的简历转换为不同的格式：

resume export resume.pdf简历导出resume.pdf

resume export resume.html简历导出resume.html

Import from LinkedIn从领英导入

One of our community members wrote a great Chrome extension to import your LinkedIn Profile. 我们的一位社区成员编写了一个很棒的 Chrome 扩展程序来导入您的 LinkedIn 个人资料。

Download here在这里下载

Hosting托管

JSON Resume offers a hosting service that renders your resume.json to any theme you would like. JSON Resume 提供托管服务，可将您的 resume.json 呈现为您喜欢的任何主题。

e.g. https://registry.jsonresume.org/thomasdavis例如https://registry.jsonresume.org/thomasdavis

All you have to do is create a Gist on GitHub named resume.json. 您所要做的就是在 GitHub 上创建一个名为 resume.json 的 Gist。

e.g. https://gist.github.com/thomasdavis/c9dcfa1b37dec07fb2ee7f36d7278105例如https://gist.github.com/thomasdavis/c9dcfa1b37dec07fb2ee7f36d7278105

Our hosting service will automatically detect this when you access https://registry.jsonresume.org/{your_github_username}当您访问 https://registry.jsonresume.org/{your_github_username} 时，我们的托管服务会自动检测到这一点

To set a theme, just add to your resume.json;要设置主题，只需添加到您的 resume.json；
{ "meta": { "theme": "elegant" } }{ “元”：{ “主题”： “优雅” } }

Schema图式

What is it?它是什么？

JSON Resume is a community driven open source initiative to create JSON-based standard for resumes. JSON Resume 是一个社区驱动的开源计划，旨在为简历创建基于 JSON 的标准。

Why JSON?为什么选择 JSON？

We believe that the strengths of the JSON format makes it a good fit for resumes. It's lightweight, easy to use and it's perfect to build tools for! 我们相信 JSON 格式的优势使其非常适合简历。它重量轻，易于使用，非常适合构建工具！

We also feel that the JSON Schema is mature enough for writing usable semantics. 我们还认为 JSON Schema 已经足够成熟，可以编写可用的语义。

Open Source开源

The schema is open source and community-driven. We release everything we do under the MIT license. 该模式是开源和社区驱动的。我们在 MIT 许可证下发布我们所做的一切。

Want to develop your own?想自己开发？

Check out an example boilerplate theme -> https://github.com/jsonresume/jsonresume-theme-boilerplate. 查看示例样板主题 -> https://github.com/jsonresume/jsonresume-theme-boilerplate。

Here is an example of a more well done and modern theme -> https://github.com/davcd/jsonresume-theme-actual. 这是一个做得更好的现代主题的示例 -> https://github.com/davcd/jsonresume-theme-actual。

For an even better theme development environment, try this -> https://github.com/kelyvin/jsonresume-theme-caffeine. 为了更好的主题开发环境，试试这个 -> https://github.com/kelyvin/jsonresume-theme-caffeine。

In short, if you want to add a theme to the official list, you need to publish an NPM module named `jsonresume-theme-{name}`. That module needs to export a function called `render` that takes a `resume.json` and returns a plain HTML string. 简而言之，如果你想将主题添加到官方列表中，你需要发布一个名为 jsonresume-theme-{name} 的 NPM 模块。该模块需要导出一个名为“render”的函数，该函数接受一个“resume.json”并返回一个纯 HTML 字符串。

Getting started入门

If you are using the registry to host your resume, you can easily test different themes by appending a query string e.g. 如果您使用注册表来托管您的简历，您可以通过附加查询字符串轻松测试不同的主题，例如

https://registry.jsonresume.org/thomasdavis?theme=flathttps://registry.jsonresume.org/thomasdavis?theme=flat

Or you can set the default theme for your resume on the registry by using the --theme option in the CLI tool e.g. 或者您可以使用 CLI 工具中的 --theme 选项在注册表中为您的简历设置默认主题，例如

resume publish --theme flat简历发布——主题平面

Community Projects社区项目

JSON Resume was built to inspire a new creative movement around resumes. This page will showcase some of those ideas… JSON Resume 旨在激发围绕简历的新创意运动。此页面将展示其中一些想法……

  • customized-registry-functions - This is a slightly tweaked version of the JSON Registry. That project is using their own Firebase project and a specific JSON schema. customized-registry-functions - 这是 JSON Registry 的一个稍微调整的版本。该项目使用他们自己的 Firebase 项目和特定的 JSON 架构。
  • registry-functions - This repository is responsible for our free JSON Resume community hosting. registry-functions - 这个存储库负责我们免费的 JSON Resume 社区托管。
  • JSON Resume as a Service - Serverless service that uses the jsonresume.org schema to generate dynamic resumes from a github gist that you can download or recieve back as a http response. JSON Resume as a Service - 无服务器服务，它使用 jsonresume.org 模式从 github 要点生成动态简历，您可以下载或作为 http 响应接收。

Import / Export进出口

  • LinkedIn Profile to JSON Resume Browser Tool - An extremely easy-to-use browser extension for exporting your full LinkedIn Profile to a JSON Resume file or string. LinkedIn Profile to JSON Resume Browser Tool - 一个非常易于使用的浏览器扩展，用于将完整的 LinkedIn Profile 导出到 JSON Resume 文件或字符串。
  • LinkedIn to JSON Résumé conversion - Inspired by https://github.com/mblarsen/resume-linkedin, deprecated primarily due to these changes in the LinkedIn API. LinkedIn 到 JSON Résumé 转换 - 受 https://github.com/mblarsen/resume-linkedin 启发，主要由于 LinkedIn API 中的这些更改而被弃用。

GithubGithub

  • JSONResume Action - GitHub Action for exporting JSONResume JSONResume Action - 用于导出 JSONResume 的 GitHub 操作

Editors编辑部

  • Profile Editor - Editor for JSON Resume Profile Editor - JSON 简历编辑器

CLI命令行界面

  • resumed - Lightweight JSON Resume builder, no-frills alternative to resume-cli. resumed - 轻量级 JSON 简历生成器，是 resume-cli 的简洁替代品。
  • resume-cli - Official CLI tool for JSON Resume resume-cli - 用于 JSON 简历的官方 CLI 工具
  • resume-pycli - Python CLI tool to build a beautiful resume from a JSON Resume file. resume-pycli - Python CLI 工具，用于从 JSON 简历文件构建漂亮的简历。

Frameworks构架

  • ng-jsonresume - ng-jsonresume lets you include a resume into a webpage by using an Angular directive and providing data in the standardized jsonresume format. ng-jsonresume - ng-jsonresume 允许您使用 Angular 指令并以标准化的 jsonresume 格式提供数据，将简历包含到网页中。
  • hugo-mod-json-resume - A Hugo module containing templates to integrate multilingual JSON Resume data into your Hugo website. hugo-mod-json-resume - 一个 Hugo 模块，包含用于将多语言 JSON 简历数据集成到您的 Hugo 网站的模板。
  • hugo-theme-gruvbox - A retro-looking Hugo theme inspired by gruvbox to build secure, fast, and SEO-ready websites. hugo-theme-gruvbox - 受 gruvbox 启发的复古外观 Hugo 主题，用于构建安全、快速和 SEO 就绪的网站。
  • gatsby-portfolio - The whole portfolio is a React-based single page app built with Gatsby v3. gatsby-portfolio - 整个产品组合是一个基于 React 的单页面应用程序，使用 Gatsby v3 构建。
  • jsonresume-manager - A Laravel framework to manage your JSON Resume's jsonresume-manager - 用于管理 JSON 简历的 Laravel 框架
  • react-ultimate-resume - react-ultimate-resume is an open-source customizable software developer resume to highlight your skills and experiences. react-ultimate-resume -react-ultimate-resume 是一种开源的可定制软件开发人员简历，可突出您的技能和经验。
  • resumis - Resumis is Esperanto for "summarized". It's also an API and headless CMS for your personal web presence, a CV generator, and JSON Resume provider. resumis - Resumis 是世界语的“总结”。它也是一个 API 和无头 CMS，用于您的个人 Web 展示、CV 生成器和 JSON 简历提供程序。
  • me - A next-gen JAMSTACK template for developers that leverage the use of JSON Resume Schema in creating a web based vitae and portfolio. me - 面向开发人员的下一代 JAMSTACK 模板，利用 JSON 简历模式创建基于 Web 的简历和投资组合。
  • netifly-jsonresume - An online résumé you can fork and host for free on GitHub quickly and without fuss. netifly-jsonresume - 在线简历，您可以在 GitHub 上快速免费地分叉和托管，而无需大惊小怪。

Visualizations可视化

  • SkillSet - Intuitive job-candidate skill visualization, taking advantage of D3.js and JSONResume. SkillSet - 直观的求职者技能可视化，利用 D3.js 和 JSONResume。
  • CMD Resume - CMD Resume is a web based command line for your resume using data from JSON Resume format. CMD Resume -CMD Resume 是一个基于 Web 的命令行，用于使用 JSON Resume 格式的数据进行简历.

Generators发电机

  • gulp-resume - gulp-resume is a gulp plugin to generate a resume using jsonresume.org. gulp-resume -gulp-resume 是一个 gulp 插件，使用 jsonresume.org 生成简历。
  • resume-generator - This project contains my personal resume or CV. It uses jsonresume hackmyresume format to save and display the resume in PDF and HTML format. resume-generator - 这个项目包含我的个人简历。它使用 jsonresume hackmyresume 格式保存和显示 PDF 和 HTML 格式的简历。

Parsers解析器

  • jsonresume (haskell) - This library encodes JSON Resume standard in Haskell datatypes, and provides a parser to read a CV in the JSON Resume format. jsonresume (haskell) - 这个库在 Haskell 数据类型中编码 JSON Resume 标准，并提供一个解析器来读取 JSON Resume 格式的 CV。

Validators验证者

  • JSON Resume Validator (PHP) - Tool in PHP that validates if a Resume is according to the defined schema. It also validates if any desired properties are not empty. JSON Resume Validator (PHP) - PHP 中的工具，用于验证简历是否符合定义的模式。它还会验证任何所需的属性是否不为空。
  • JSON Resume Validator (Python) - Python tool to validate JSON resumes to ensure that they are according to the defined schema JSON Resume Validator (Python) - 用于验证 JSON 简历以确保它们符合定义的模式的 Python 工具
  • JSON Resume Validator and Parser (Java) - Java library to validate and parse JSON resumes to Java objects JSON Resume Validator and Parser (Java) - 用于验证 JSON 简历并将其解析为 Java 对象的 Java 库
  • JSON Resume Validator (Go) - Go library to validate JSON resumes JSON Resume Validator (Go) - 用于验证 JSON 简历的 Go 库

Machine Learning机器学习

  • jsonresume-gpt3 - This uses GPT-3 API access to generate fake resumes. jsonresume-gpt3 - 这使用 GPT-3 API 访问来生成假简历。

Contributing贡献

  • We need everyone to start making themes我们需要每个人都开始制作主题
  • People who can offer advice on the standard可以就标准提供建议的人
  • The standard should be able to export to any format under the sun该标准应该能够在阳光下导出为任何格式

News, features and releases新闻、功能和发布

5th Birthday and New Features 5 岁生日和新功能

posted June 27, 2019 发表于 2019 年 6 月 27 日

It was our 5th birthday last week and we are happy to announce some new features. Development has been slow. In retrospect this is a good thing for something that purports to be a standard. We didn’t make any radical changes which kept the ecosystem stable. The community still exists due to many members contributing above and beyond. We extend thanks to people have written themes, parsers, converters, tools and services. The website will soon showcase the plethora of projects built around JSON Resume.上周是我们 5 岁生日，我们很高兴宣布一些新功能。发展一直很缓慢。回想起来，这对于声称是标准的东西来说是一件好事。我们没有做出任何根本性的改变来保持生态系统的稳定。由于许多成员的贡献，社区仍然存在。我们感谢人们编写了主题、解析器、转换器、工具和服务。该网站将很快展示围绕 JSON Resume 构建的大量项目。

News, features and releases新闻、功能和发布

First Official Release 首次正式发布

posted July 31, 2014 2014 年 7 月 31 日发布

It has been just over three weeks since JSON resume first went public, and we are proud to announce the first official version of the specification. After much consideration we decided to launch the first version as 0.0.0, which assumes everything up until this point was conceptual, and thus no backwards compatibility has been built out.距离 JSON resume 首次公开已经过去了三个多星期，我们很自豪地宣布该规范的第一个正式版本。经过深思熟虑，我们决定将第一个版本发布为 0.0.0，它假设到目前为止的一切都是概念性的，因此没有建立向后兼容性。

Unfortunately this means that if you created a resume before this release, most parts of the ecosystem will not work for you. Though there weren’t too many changes so visit the specification page and update your resume.json accordingly.不幸的是，这意味着如果您在此版本之前创建了简历，则生态系统的大部分部分将不适合您。虽然没有太多变化，但请访问规范页面并相应地更新您的 resume.json。

Make sure you reinstall the latest version of the CLI tool by typing sudo npm install -g resume-cli into terminal. Once installed, you can also take advantage of the resume test command to test if your resume.json is compatible with version 0.0.0.通过在终端中键入 sudo npm install -g resume-cli 确保重新安装最新版本的 CLI 工具。安装后，您还可以利用 resume test 命令来测试您的 resume.json 是否与版本 0.0.0 兼容。

For a full list of changes, view the README for the resume schema repo.有关更改的完整列表，请查看 resume schema repo 的 README。

Just because this is an official release of the specification, it doesn’t guarantee that the ecosystem is stable. We actually had to wait for this official release before we could lock down parts of the ecosystem.仅仅因为这是规范的正式发布，并不能保证生态系统是稳定的。实际上，在我们锁定部分生态系统之前，我们不得不等待这个正式版本。

How are we doing?我们怎么样？

When JSON resume first went public, it was actually unexpected and the project wasn’t quite as mature as we would have liked it to have been. In the days following the leak, the homepage received over 50,000 visitors and a lot of people reached out offering support. We worked overtime to get people hacking away at different areas of the project.当 JSON resume 首次公开时，实际上是出乎意料的，该项目并没有我们希望的那么成熟。在泄密事件发生后的几天里，该主页的访问量超过了 50,000 人，并且有很多人伸出援手提供支持。我们加班加点地让人们在项目的不同领域进行黑客攻击。

Some accomplishments so far目前取得的一些成绩

  • Over 1400 stars on the resume CLI简历 CLI 上超过 1400 颗星
  • 97 issues created for the specification, 52 closed为规范创建了 97 个问题，52 个已关闭
  • Built a modular theme system leveraging NPM for version management构建了一个模块化的主题系统，利用 NPM 进行版本管理
  • Active theme development underway活动主题开发正在进行中
  • Progress made on LinkedIn exportLinkedIn 导出取得的进展
  • Build your resume.json with a GUI, coming in the next few days(screenshot)使用 GUI 构建你的 resume.json，将在接下来的几天内发布（截图）
  • Organized a standards committee组织标准委员会
  • Multiple HR related services are looking at supporting and potentially sponsoring the JSON resume project多项人力资源相关服务正在考虑支持并可能赞助 JSON 简历项目
  • Officially listed JSON schema on JSON Schema Store在 JSON Schema Store 上正式列出 JSON schema

An obligatory thank you to everybody who has participated up to this point. And a very special thanks to Mattias Erming who has put a lot of hard work into developing and brainstorming the future of JSON resume.必须感谢到目前为止参与的每一个人。非常特别感谢 Mattias Erming，他为开发和集思广益 JSON 简历的未来付出了大量努力。

Where are we heading?我们要去哪里？

After long discussions about the specification in the GitHub issues, we have come to settle on a few points.在 GitHub 问题中对规范进行了长时间的讨论之后，我们已经确定了几点。

  • JSON resume exist to empower individuals to manage their job seeking profiles and this is our highest priority.JSON 简历的存在是为了让个人能够管理他们的求职档案，这是我们的首要任务。
  • Because there is no easily accessible alternative, we are going to maintain a casual approach to the project.因为没有容易获得的替代方案，我们将对项目保持一种随意的方法。
  • The specification is not to be the perfect description of a person but instead a description of a resume where only things relevant in the context of hiring will be allowed in.规范不是对一个人的完美描述，而是对简历的描述，其中只允许包含与招聘相关的内容。

To guarantee the success of JSON resume, we will be aiming to integrate as an import/export option where ever possible. We want a thriving theme ecosystem and as many tools as possible.为了保证 JSON 简历的成功，我们的目标是尽可能集成为导入/导出选项。我们想要一个繁荣的主题生态系统和尽可能多的工具。

Please leave your feedback and ideas below! Also, please join the movement!请在下方留下您的反馈和想法！另外，请加入运动！

By Thomas Davis and Roland Sharp托马斯·戴维斯和罗兰·夏普

Announcing our first service integration 宣布我们的第一个服务集成

posted September 09, 2014 发布于 2014 年 9 月 9 日

Since the inception of JSON Resume in July we have had a vast number of services reach out expressing their interest in supporting JSON Resume.自从 JSON Resume 在 7 月份推出以来，我们已经有大量服务表达了他们对支持 JSON Resume 的兴趣。

One of those companies was called Represent, whose lead developer Jordan Singer emailed me earlier this week announcing their integration.其中一家名为 Represent 的公司，其首席开发人员 Jordan Singer 本周早些时候给我发了一封电子邮件，宣布了他们的整合。

So far they have only added support for exporting to JSON Resume, but we hope that in the future users can simply upload their resume.json to the service instead of filling out their profile manually.到目前为止，他们只添加了对导出到 JSON Resume 的支持，但我们希望将来用户可以简单地将他们的 resume.json 上传到该服务，而不是手动填写他们的个人资料。

You can see an example export at https://represent.io/jordan.json您可以在 https://represent.io/jordan.json 查看示例导出

We have also added an Integrations page that we hope will fill up quickly.我们还添加了一个集成页面，我们希望它能很快填满。

Make sure you reach out and ask your favorite services to support JSON Resume!请务必联系并要求您最喜欢的服务支持 JSON Resume！

5th Birthday and New Features 5 岁生日和新功能

posted June 27, 2019 发表于 2019 年 6 月 27 日

It was our 5th birthday last week and we are happy to announce some new features. Development has been slow. In retrospect this is a good thing for something that purports to be a standard. We didn’t make any radical changes which kept the ecosystem stable. The community still exists due to many members contributing above and beyond. We extend thanks to people have written themes, parsers, converters, tools and services. The website will soon showcase the plethora of projects built around JSON Resume.上周是我们 5 岁生日，我们很高兴宣布一些新功能。发展一直很缓慢。回想起来，这对于声称是标准的东西来说是一件好事。我们没有做出任何根本性的改变来保持生态系统的稳定。由于许多成员的贡献，社区仍然存在。我们感谢人们编写了主题、解析器、转换器、工具和服务。该网站将很快展示围绕 JSON Resume 构建的大量项目。

The last year has been unstable when it came to the free hosting and themes server. Maintaining the servers cost and development has always been a thorn in our sides. We’ve finally managed to rewrite those servers into a much more manageable solution.去年在免费托管和主题服务器方面一直不稳定。维护服务器成本和开发一直是我们的眼中钉。我们终于设法将这些服务器重写为更易于管理的解决方案。

Hosting托管

Our new system leverages serverless hosting which means we don’t have to SSH into our old box at 3am because of logs killing our disk space.我们的新系统利用无服务器托管，这意味着我们不必在凌晨 3 点通过 SSH 连接到我们的旧机器，因为日志会占用我们的磁盘空间。

We’ve also deprecated our user/resume storage in favour of users storing their resumes as Gist on their own Github accounts.我们还弃用了我们的用户/简历存储，以支持用户将他们的简历作为 Gist 存储在他们自己的 Github 帐户中。

You can take advantage of our new hosting您可以利用我们的新主机

e.g. https://registry.jsonresume.org/thomasdavis例如https://registry.jsonresume.org/thomasdavis

by simply creating a Gist on your Github with the filename being resume.json通过简单地在你的 Github 上创建一个文件名为 resume.json 的 Gist

e.g. https://gist.github.com/thomasdavis/c9dcfa1b37dec07fb2ee7f36d7278105例如https://gist.github.com/thomasdavis/c9dcfa1b37dec07fb2ee7f36d7278105

That is all you need to do, and you can view your resume at这就是您需要做的全部，您可以在以下位置查看您的简历

https://registry.jsonresume.org/{your_github_username}https://registry.jsonresume.org/{your_github_username}

To change the default theme, simply add a top level property to your resume.json要更改默认主题，只需将顶级属性添加到您的 resume.json

{ "meta": { "theme": "kendall" } }"{ “元”：{ “主题”： “肯德尔” } }”

The theme server is whitelisted now meaning that only approved themes will work on the registry.主题服务器现在已列入白名单，这意味着只有经过批准的主题才能在注册表中运行。

You can suggest one on our ongoing issue -> https://github.com/jsonresume/theme-functions/issues/12您可以就我们正在进行的问题提出建议 -> https://github.com/jsonresume/theme-functions/issues/12

Gist are great;要点很棒；

  • Versioned版本化
  • You won’t lose your resume unless Github shuts down除非 Github 关闭，否则你不会丢失你的简历
  • You can use their online editor for quick updates您可以使用他们的在线编辑器进行快速更新

A bunch of people have already migrated to the new system and we believe it to be a great step in the right direction.很多人已经迁移到新系统，我们相信这是朝着正确方向迈出的重要一步。
